{"tid":2339740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"住緊劏房，你問我答","createTime":"2020-12-25T01:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T18:11:29.000Z","uid":252031,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0ee2cf3ad85b8a2079a6d8a8c8d4bef6680eda","tid":2339740,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:41:10.000Z","msg":"Lonely Christmas 上連登圍吓爐先<br />\n唔想自爆儘量答"},{"pid":"e53b24680079c364c3d9d3904d9a7777c635f23a","tid":2339740,"uid":308264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:42:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eefa8a4f3b78c7834678384f8546f2f79bd2585c","tid":2339740,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:43:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a55ded421763a33ca0ff65eedce0353adf4c274","tid":2339740,"uid":252031,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:45:33.000Z","msg":"咁一條友住有乜好就係人都知啦<br />\n講吓有乜唔好啦<br />\n- 收工返嚟要諗食乜<br />\n- 定期要去買下日用品<br />\n- 家務一腳踢<br />\n- 病咗無人照顧你<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗到呢堆嘢好簡單，其實返咗一日工已經好攰，做得慢嘅話，搞掂堆嘢已經好夜<br />\n真係要定心理準備"},{"pid":"0853a452699d90d59823cad43cc88ff364f62729","tid":2339740,"uid":252031,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eefa8a4f3b78c7834678384f8546f2f79bd2585c","tid":2339740,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:43:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:46:46.000Z","msg":"一個角落頭，有齊雪櫃，洗衣機，櫥櫃，洗手盆，抽氣綫，不過都幾窄"},{"pid":"b6469cebf187aa6e69c7523382df9a5f454b59c8","tid":2339740,"uid":252031,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e53b24680079c364c3d9d3904d9a7777c635f23a","tid":2339740,"uid":308264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:42:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:49:36.000Z","msg":"我就睇咗好多間嘅，依家疫情之下啲租平咗，我比你估下我租咗邊間<br />\n1. 6000包水電，150呎，5分鐘到地鐵<br />\n2. 5500包水電，130呎，3分鐘到地鐵<br />\n3. 4500不包水電，100呎，8分鐘到地鐵<br />\n4. 6000包水電，100呎，5分鐘到地鐵"},{"pid":"d246ed7827